# Logging

`import logger from "@/lib/logger"` — never `console.log`.

```typescript
logger.error("Message", {
  metadata: { storeId, error: err instanceof Error ? err.message : String(err) },
  tags: ["domain", "error"],
});
```

No secrets in logs. Match catch variable names in metadata.
